### Building from Source

```bash
# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/mexyusef/zscheduler.git
cd zscheduler

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Run from source
python run.py                    # GUI
python -m zscheduler_app.cli.cli # CLI

# Build package
python -m build

# Install locally
pip install dist/zscheduler-*.whl
```

